\/hot\/498ed5fbb68773c3_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ww4.sinaimg.cn\/thumb180\/001N9Ovwly1gxiaedmpsdj60m80m840c02.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/498ed5fbb68773c3_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#长沙疫情#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">#长沙疫情#【#长沙检出2例入境奥密克戎感染者#】湖南疾病预防控制中心对12月16日长沙市境外输入新冠病毒感染者呼吸道标本进行新冠病毒全基因组测序和序列分析，经中国疾病预防控制中心复核，均确认检出新冠病毒奥密克戎变异株（B.1.1.529进化分支）。该2例新冠病毒奥密克戎变异株感染者系入境闭环管控 ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n    <div class=\"UG_box_foot\">\n        <a href=\"\/\/weibo.com\/a\/hot\/realtime\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">查看更多<i class=\"W_ficon ficon_arrow_right S_ficon\">a<\/i><\/a>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n"})</script>
